7HCC Digital Meeting http://sevenhillscame...

Since many of you are members of the 7HCC this is an invite to other Meetup members who might have a special interest in all things to do with digital photography.

Monthly meeting of the Seven Hills Camera Club's Digital Group. We discuss many topics of digital photography.

Location: Banx Room - Main Library

Contact: Don Roberts 508-867-6498 onsouthpond@charter.net
